<span style="color: #0000ff;">修改为以下代码，则调用指定任一子栏目文章列表显示正常：</span>
<pre>if(!preg_match('#,#', $typeid)) {
    $tpsql = " id IN($typeid) AND ispart&lt;&gt;2 AND ishidden&lt;&gt;1 ";
}
else {
    $tpsql = " id IN($typeid) AND ispart&lt;&gt;2 AND ishidden&lt;&gt;1 ";
